text: Carl Wiegand (born 1 August 1877) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
